This is a collection of various scripts for processing multimedia files.

All code and documentation is in the Public Domain. So you can do with it
whatever you want.

== tag ==
Script in Python for processing metadata.

Dependencies:
 Mutagen - http://code.google.com/p/mutagen/
 PythonMusicBrainz2 - http://musicbrainz.org/doc/PythonMusicBrainz2

== togg ==
Script in Scheme for recoding various audiofiles to OGG Vorbis.

Dependencies:
 Scheme implementation: Gauche Scheme

 Shntool - http://etree.org/shnutils/shntool/

 libdca for DTS recoding (optional) -
   http://www.videolan.org/developers/libdca.html

== rj ==
Removing junk from filenames.

Dependencies:
 Scheme implementation: Gauche Scheme
